      <abstract>
        <p>We report the synthesis of [(3-chlorobenzamido)methyl]triethylammonium chloride in a reaction of <italic>N</italic>-(chloromethyl)-3-chlorobenzamide and triethylamine in dry acetone. The structure of the newly synthesized compound was characterized with <sup>1</sup>H-NMR, <sup>13</sup>C-NMR, FTIR and Mass spectroscopy.</p>
      </abstract>
